---
layout: "base.njk"
title: "Contacto"
description: "Hablemos de tu proyecto. Contacta con Visión MS Producción Audiovisual para cotizar tu boda, evento o proyecto corporativo."
---

<style>
    .contact-wrapper { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr; gap: 50px; }
    .contact-form h3 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .form-group label { display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: 600; }
    .form-group input, .form-group select, .form-group textarea { width: 100%; padding: 15px; border: 1px solid #ccc; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 1rem; font-family: var(--fuente-texto); }
    .contact-info { background-color: var(--color-fondo-claro); padding: 40px; border-radius: 10px; }
    .contact-info h3 { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .contact-info p { margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .info-item { display: flex; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1rem; }
    .info-item a { color: var(--color-texto-oscuro); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; transition: color 0.3s;}
    .info-item a:hover { color: var(--color-rojo-principal); }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { .contact-wrapper { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>

<main>
    <section class="page-header" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), url('/images/retrato-9.jpg');" data-aos="fade-in">
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Hablemos.</h1>
            <p style="font-size: 1.2rem;">Estamos listos para escuchar tu idea y convertirla en una realidad visual.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact-main">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="contact-wrapper">
                <div class="contact-form" data-aos="fade-right">
                    <h3>Envíanos un Mensaje</h3>
                    <p>Completa el formulario y te responderemos en menos de 24 horas.</p>
                    <form name="contact" method="POST" data-netlify="true" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                         <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="contact" />
                        <div class="form-group"><label for="name">Nombre Completo</label><input type="text" id="name" name="name" required></div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label for="email">Correo Electrónico</label><input type="email" id="email" name="email" required></div>
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="inquiry-type">Tipo de Consulta</label>
                            <select id="inquiry-type" name="inquiry-type">
                                <option value="evento-social">Evento Social / Boda</option>
                                <option value="servicio-empresa">Servicio para Empresa</option>
                                <option value="produccion-vivo">Producción en Vivo</option>
                                <option value="general">Consulta General</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-group"><label for="message">Tu Mensaje</label><textarea id="message" name="message" rows="6" required></textarea></div>
                        <button type="submit" class="btn">Enviar Mensaje</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="contact-info" data-aos="fade-left" data-aos-delay="200">
                    <h3>Información de Contacto</h3>
                    <p>También puedes contactarnos directamente.</p>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <svg class="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path d="M48 64C21.5 64 0 85.5 0 112c0 15.1 7.1 29.3 19.2 38.4L236.8 313.6c11.4 8.5 27 8.5 38.4 0L492.8 150.4c12.1-9.1 19.2-23.3 19.2-38.4c0-26.5-21.5-48-48-48H48zM0 176V384c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64H448c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V176L294.4 339.2c-22.8 17.1-54 17.1-76.8 0L0 176z"/></svg>
                        <a href="mailto:{{ sitio.email }}">{{ sitio.email }}</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <svg class="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path d="M164.9 24.6c-7.7-18.6-28-28.5-47.4-23.2l-88 24C12.1 30.2 0 46 0 64C0 311.4 200.6 512 448 512c18 0 33.8-12.1 38.6-29.5l24-88c5.3-19.4-4.6-39.7-23.2-47.4l-96-40c-16.3-6.8-35.2-2.2-46.2 11.5l-39.8 49.9c-5.8 7.2-15.8 9.2-24.1 5.7c-52.1-21.2-92.7-61.8-113.9-113.9c-3.5-8.3-1.4-18.3 5.7-24.1l49.9-39.8c13.7-10.9 18.3-30 11.5-46.2l-40-96z"/></svg>
                        <a href="tel:{{ sitio.telefono }}">{{ sitio.telefono }}</a>
                    </div>
                    <h3 style="margin-top: 40px;">Síguenos</h3>
                    <div class="info-item">
                       <svg class="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 448 512"><path d="M224.1 141c-63.6 0-114.9 51.3-114.9 114.9s51.3 114.9 114.9 114.9S339 319.5 339 255.9 287.7 141 224.1 141zm0 189.6c-41.1 0-74.7-33.5-74.7-74.7s33.5-74.7 74.7-74.7 74.7 33.5 74.7 74.7-33.6 74.7-74.7 74.7zm146.4-194.3c0 14.9-12 26.8-26.8 26.8-14.9 0-26.8-12-26.8-26.8s12-26.8 26.8-26.8 26.8 12 26.8 26.8zm76.1 27.2c-1.7-35.9-9.9-67.7-36.2-93.9-26.2-26.2-58-34.4-93.9-36.2-37.2-2.1-147.9-2.1-185.1 0-35.9 1.7-67.7 9.9-93.9 36.1s-34.4 58-36.2 93.9c-2.1 37.2-2.1 147.9 0 185.1 1.7 35.9 9.9 67.7 36.2 93.9 26.3 26.2 58 34.4 93.9 36.2 37.2 2.1 147.9 2.1 185.1 0 35.9-1.7 67.7-9.9 93.9-36.2 26.2-26.2 34.4-58 36.2-93.9 2.1-37.2 2.1-147.8 0-185.1z"/></svg>
                       <a href="{{ sitio.instagram_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Instagram</a>
                    </div>
                     <div class="info-item">
                        <svg class="icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 576 512"><path d="M549.655 124.083c-6.281-23.65-24.787-42.276-48.284-48.597C458.781 64 288 64 288 64S117.22 64 74.629 75.486c-23.497 6.322-42.003 24.947-48.284 48.597-11.412 42.867-11.412 132.305-11.412 132.305s0 89.438 11.412 132.305c6.281 23.65 24.787 42.276 48.284 48.597C117.22 448 288 448 288 448s170.78 0 213.371-11.486c23.497-6.322 42.003-24.947 48.284-48.597 11.412-42.867 11.412-132.305 11.412-132.305s0-89.438-11.412-132.305zM232.615 354.708V157.292L354.814 256l-122.199 98.708z"/></svg>
                        <a href="{{ sitio.youtube_url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">YouTube</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
